# Private same-class generic method (invokespecial) arg cast: the (V) cast on the Object argument to
# `this.sink(...)` must be re-synthesized. invokespecial whose target IS the current class is a
# private same-class call, not a super.m() call. Fix: sameClassMethodParamType +
# JDEC_GENERIC_SELFMETHOD_PRIVATE_OFF sub-switch (guava AbstractBiMap.updateInverseMap family).
+/this\.sink\(var1,\(V\)\(/
-this.sink(var1,var2)
